These are the facts:<br>
-Enchanters, a class which <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>should</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> be doing roughly paladin level damage, should not be doing chain-nuking-wizard, chain-nuking-mage and pet, or end-game-rogue-vs-green-trash damage. <br>
